data.description: Located in beautiful gated Beaver Creek Preserve. This new home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage. Open floorplan with great room concept. Kitchen features Stainless Steel appliances including electric range, dishwasher and Microwave. Laundry has upper cabinets. Pre plumbed soft water/water filtration.
